h1 FreeCodeCamp: URL Shortener Microservice
blockquote
  p User stories:
  ul
    li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
    li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.

h3 Example creation usage:
code https://micurl.herokuapp.com/new/https://www.google.com

br
code https://micurl.herokuapp.com/new/http://foo.com:80

h3 Example creation output
code {"original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"http://micurl.herokuapp.com/HJcn_29Eb"}


h3 Usage:
code https://micurl.herokuapp.com/HkSTLh5VW

